1. Wait until the publish job is finished and the artifacts are up in the Maven Central.

   - Publish job: https://github.com/line/centraldogma/actions/workflows/publish-release.yml
   - Sonatype repository: https://oss.sonatype.org/
   - Maven Central: https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/com/linecorp/centraldogma/centraldogma-bom/${releaseVersion}/
   - Site job: https://github.com/line/centraldogma/actions/workflows/publish-site.yml

2. Close the milestone and set its release date at:

   https://github.com/line/centraldogma/milestones

3. Update the release note at:

   https://github.com/line/centraldogma/releases/tag/${tag}
